5:
Is Palpebra undergoing renovation?
I can hardly recognize it.
10:
Beautiful, isn't she? We're dressing
the city up in her holiday clothes.
17:
Well, yeah! 'Tis the season and all
that. It's not a party without tinsel,
candles, and mistletoe everywhere
you turn.
20:
And would you look at the
presents!\n
Now, don't even get me started on
how I had to beg and wheedle a
budget out of the Guildmasters.
Bunch of old Scrooges...
30:
What in the name of the holiday
ghost?!
38: It's over... The holidays are ruined...
42:
So, those monsters made off with all
the presents?
54:
That's 'cause they STOLE our holiday
joy! The annual present raffle's the
hottest event of the season!
57:
Come to think of it... isn't the raffle
funded by fees you forcibly collect
from adventurers?
61:
Careful, Alk. Your words may come
back to haunt you...
68:
Guess the Guild'll just have to host a
new event!
76: You mean like duck hunting season?!
78:
For every golem butt you kick, you'll
get a fantabulous present from the
Guild!
81:
Wait... So you're sending us out to
beat up golems... so that we can
give you the presents they stole... to
give to us?
84:
You got a problem, bub? I'll have
you know this was all according to
keikaku.
90:
Alk, we cannot let these thieves run
free. There is justice to be served.
98:
Watch out, golems! We're taking
back our holiday cheer!
